                  <persname>Christopher Morley</persname></unittitle>
            <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1943 Sep 15</unitdate>
            <physdesc>
              <genreform>TLS,</genreform>
              <extent>1 p.</extent>
            </physdesc>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>[Expresses his appreciation as well as 
                  <persname>Jesse Stuart</persname>'s and that of
                  everyone at 
                  <corpname>E. P. Dutton &amp; Co.</corpname>, Inc. for
                  Morley's choosing Stuart's novel 
                  <bibref xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="">Taps for Private Tussie</bibref>for the
                  December selection of the 
                  <corpname>Book of the Month Club</corpname>; mentions
                  Stuart's work in the cornfield, cut in his leg, and
                  poor financial condition.]</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
